{"tid":1250942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩個公僕團體要求麥美娟澄清曾否以粗言辱罵行政長官","createTime":"2019-06-22T09:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T10:17:03.000Z","uid":38651,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"08cc5fd4b8f648df979598b54450de090b53634b","tid":1250942,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:46:05.000Z","msg":"政府華員會及公務員工會聯合會要求工聯會立法會議員麥美娟澄清，有無在6月15日行政長官林鄭月娥會見部分議員時，以粗言辱罵行政長官，如確有其事，應向行政長官公開道歉。<br />\n<br />\n工會表示，任何公職人員，包括行政長官，各司局長，各級公務員等，在執行職務時，不應受任何語言暴力侵犯，又指議員理應作為港人，尤其是年輕人及兒童的表率。<br />\n<br />\n兩個工會又說，他們的行動，只涉反對語言暴力，不針對任何政黨，不涉及任何政黨政治，不涉及任何有關修訂《逃犯條例》爭議。<br />\n<br />\n鬼打鬼到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3401f32fe227cf0bb2318444432f20e7738caf0","tid":1250942,"uid":77717,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:46:56.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2de1168fb8327610d68a17b38d524c8233261dc","tid":1250942,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"圍困警總人士學了美娟"},{"pid":"c105c2bf971957f69eeb4f64b4f66b1ac262a868","tid":1250942,"uid":123562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:03:43.000Z","msg":"舉中指算啦 唔好講粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5632a8d9b6cb242084684f2fa2d4c6fc5712aa","tid":1250942,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:06:39.000Z","msg":"道你老母"},{"pid":"342ee0a630d80dc925b04fdc9527e3759ae7bdb3","tid":1250942,"uid":153827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"如果打人唔犯法，應該會見到兩隻怪獸打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,宜家講緊關系到佢地選情喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f5